#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:2
msgid "lmcache trace"
msgstr "lmcache 跟踪"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache trace`` command inspects and replays LMCache storage-level "
"trace files (``.lct``). It has two sub-commands:"
msgstr "``lmcache trace`` 命令用于检查和重放 LMCache 存储级别的跟踪文件 (``.lct``)。它有两个子命令："

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:13
msgid ""
"``lmcache trace`` needs the full ``lmcache`` package (StorageManager, "
"trace codecs, ``TraceReader``). It is not available in the lightweight "
"``lmcache-cli`` install and exits with status ``2`` if those modules are "
"missing."
msgstr "``lmcache trace`` 需要完整的 ``lmcache`` 包（StorageManager、trace 编解码器、``TraceReader``）。在轻量级的 ``lmcache-cli`` 安装中不可用，如果缺少这些模块，则会以状态 ``2`` 退出。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:18
msgid ""
"Trace *capture* is not a ``trace`` sub-command — recording is bound to a "
"live server via ``lmcache server --trace-level storage [--trace-output "
"...]`` (see :doc:`server`)."
msgstr "Trace *捕获* 不是 ``trace`` 子命令 — 录制绑定到通过 ``lmcache server --trace-level storage [--trace-output ...]`` 的实时服务器（参见 :doc:`server`）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:24
msgid "info"
msgstr "信息"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:26
msgid ""
"Print a one-screen summary of a trace file: header metadata plus per-"
"qualname record counts."
msgstr "打印跟踪文件的一屏摘要：头部元数据加上每个 qualname 的记录计数。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:46
msgid ""
"The only argument is the positional ``FILE`` (path to a ``.lct`` trace "
"file)."
msgstr "唯一的参数是位置参数 ``FILE``（指向 ``.lct`` 跟踪文件的路径）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:50
msgid "replay"
msgstr "重放"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:52
msgid ""
"Reissue every recorded call against a fresh ``StorageManager``, honoring "
"the recorded inter-call timings."
msgstr "对新创建的 ``StorageManager`` 重新发出每个记录的调用，遵循记录的调用间隔时间。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:60
msgid ""
"``replay`` accepts the standard storage-manager configuration flags "
"(``--l1-size-gb``, ``--eviction-policy``, ``--l2-...``); see ``lmcache "
"server --help`` for the full list. The replay-side config may differ from"
" the config recorded in the trace, which can legitimately cause retrieve "
"misses."
msgstr "``replay`` 接受标准的存储管理器配置标志（``--l1-size-gb``, ``--eviction-policy``, ``--l2-...``）；有关完整列表，请参见 ``lmcache server --help``。重放侧的配置可能与记录在追踪中的配置不同，这可能会导致合法的查找未命中。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:68
msgid ""
"A replay environment mismatch may cause retrieve misses. Replay uses the "
"replay-side StorageManager config (which may differ from the recorded "
"config), runs on a host whose performance may differ from the recording "
"host, and StorageManager reads/writes are async. Treat retrieve-miss "
"counts as a signal about the replay environment, not a defect in the "
"trace."
msgstr "重放环境不匹配可能导致查找未命中。重放使用重放端的 StorageManager 配置（可能与记录的配置不同），在性能可能与记录主机不同的主机上运行，并且 StorageManager 的读/写是异步的。将查找未命中计数视为重放环境的信号，而不是记录中的缺陷。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:75
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:81
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:82
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:83
msgid "``FILE``"
msgstr "``FILE``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:84
msgid "Path to a ``.lct`` trace file (positional, required)."
msgstr "```.lct``` 跟踪文件的路径（位置参数，必填）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:85
msgid "``--verbose``"
msgstr "``--verbose``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:86
msgid "Print one line per replayed record."
msgstr "每个重放记录打印一行。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:87
msgid "``--jsonl-out PATH``"
msgstr "``--jsonl-out PATH``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:88
msgid ""
"Write one JSON object per replayed record to ``PATH`` (qualname, "
"latency_ms, failed)."
msgstr "将每个重放记录写入一个 JSON 对象到 ``PATH``（qualname，延迟_ms，失败）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:90
msgid "``--output-dir DIR``"
msgstr "``--output-dir DIR``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:91
msgid ""
"Directory for aggregated CSV / JSON summary output (default: current "
"directory)."
msgstr "聚合的 CSV / JSON 摘要输出目录（默认：当前目录）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:93
msgid "``--no-csv``"
msgstr "``--no-csv``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:94
msgid "Skip the aggregated CSV summary export."
msgstr "跳过聚合的 CSV 摘要导出。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:95
msgid "``--json``"
msgstr "``--json``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:96
msgid "Also export an aggregated JSON summary."
msgstr "还可以导出一个汇总的 JSON。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:97
msgid "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"
msgstr "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:98
msgid "Suppress the terminal metrics table (files are still written)."
msgstr "抑制终端指标表（文件仍然会被写入）。"

#: ../../source/cli/trace.rst:100
msgid ""
"The terminal summary reports overall replay stats (records replayed / "
"skipped / failed, duration, config-digest match) and per-op latency "
"percentiles. ``replay`` exits with status ``1`` if any record failed."
msgstr "终端摘要报告整体重放统计信息（重放/跳过/失败的记录、持续时间、配置摘要匹配）和每个操作的延迟百分位数。如果任何记录失败，``replay`` 将以状态 ``1`` 退出。"

